cff-version: 1.2.0
message: "If you use GRACE in your research, please cite it as below."
type: software
title: "GRACE: Genomic Repeat Analysis and Characterisation Engine"
abstract: >
  GRACE is a standalone, offline, cross-platform desktop application for
  SSR (microsatellite) marker development. It integrates SSR detection,
  Primer3-based primer design, quality filtering, BLAST-based specificity
  validation, and lab-ready CSV export in a single graphical interface
  requiring no command-line interaction.
authors:
